<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Modern — Games Landing</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f5f4f0;
    --bg-2: #eceae3;
    --ink: #131214;
    --muted: #6b6a72;
    --line: rgba(19, 18, 20, 0.08);
    --accent: #1a1a1a;
    --pop: #ff5a3c;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Inter", "SF Pro Display", -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 10%, #ffe7e0 0%, transparent 45%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 90%, #e0e8ff 0%, transparent 50%),
      var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 64px 32px 96px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  header {
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto 64px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 84px);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }
  h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--pop); }
  .lead {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 22px 0 0;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  nav { margin-top: 28px; }
  nav a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .grid {
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.62);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 18px 20px 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.8) inset, 0 12px 40px -20px rgba(19,18,20,0.18);
    transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), box-shadow 0.35s;
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.8) inset, 0 22px 60px -22px rgba(19,18,20,0.28);
  }
  .shot {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e9e6df, #d3d0c7);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .row {
    display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .idx {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .prompt {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #2c2b30;
    min-height: 90px;
  }
  .play {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .play::after { content: "→"; transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .play:hover::after { transform: translateX(3px); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="eyebrow">Modern · Series 04</div>
    <h1>Quiet games for <em>thoughtful</em> moments.</h1>
    <p class="lead">A small collection of six minimalist mini-games. Soft palettes, gentle motion, and just enough challenge to make a coffee break feel deliberate.</p>
    <nav><a href="index.html">← All themes</a></nav>
  </header>

  <main class="grid">
    <article class="card">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/pair-flip"><img class="shot" src="https://pair-flip--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <div class="row"><h2>Tile Fold</h2><span class="idx">01 / 06</span></div>
      <p class="prompt">A 4×4 grid of pastel cards. Flip two, match removes the pair. Time tracked, glass-morphism UI, gentle haptics.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/pair-flip">Open</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/arc-strike"><img class="shot" src="https://arc-strike--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <div class="row"><h2>Orbit Dot</h2><span class="idx">02 / 06</span></div>
      <p class="prompt">A dot orbits the center. Tap as it crosses the target arc; the arc shrinks each round. Streaks award bonuses.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/arc-strike">Open</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/color-cascade"><img class="shot" src="https://color-cascade--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <div class="row"><h2>Color Merge</h2><span class="idx">03 / 06</span></div>
      <p class="prompt">A 2048-style swipe merger. Combining same-colored tiles evolves their hue along a smooth gradient toward a final color.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/color-cascade">Open</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/lane-drop"><img class="shot" src="https://lane-drop--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <div class="row"><h2>Rhythm Tap</h2><span class="idx">04 / 06</span></div>
      <p class="prompt">Three falling-note lanes, sixty-second song. Tap the matching key as each note hits the bar. Crisp particle feedback per hit.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/lane-drop">Open</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/zen-geometry"><img class="shot" src="https://zen-geometry--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <div class="row"><h2>Zen Shape</h2><span class="idx">05 / 06</span></div>
      <p class="prompt">Drag basic shapes into silhouettes to fill them. Twenty short puzzles, no timer, no fail state — just a soft, ambient flow.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/zen-geometry">Open</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/color-connect"><img class="shot" src="https://color-connect--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <div class="row"><h2>Flow Link</h2><span class="idx">06 / 06</span></div>
      <p class="prompt">Connect colored dot pairs on a grid with non-crossing paths that cover every cell. Twelve hand-tuned levels of rising challenge.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/color-connect">Open</a>
    </article>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
{{> newsletter}}
